{
  "texts": [
    "• Whole Win/Loss Rule: The overall win/loss conditions.",
    "A sample template can be found in A.2.",
    "Several works (Zha et al., 2019; Guo et al., 2023) note that game states are represented using low-level numerical values in most imperfect information game environments.",
    "LLMs can convert these atomic game states into human-readable text (Wu et al., 2023; Wang et al., 2023; Guo et al., 2022; 2023), enhancing the model's understanding.",
    "Therefore, we structure the observation rule and game history conversion rules similarly to game rules to help LLM convert low-level current state and history information to readable text."
  ]
}